name: Volume 3

description:
Kazuma, an Alter who uses his powers for mercenary work and the occasional heist, keeps himself out of the spotlight, providing for himself and his ward, Kanami, in the wastelands of the Lost Grounds, away from the fledgling cities that have begun to sprout from the ruins of the former Yokohama. But when he crosses paths with one of the most fervent officers of HOLY, Ryohu--an Alter himself who has decided to help bring other Alters into HOLY under the auspices of order and justice--Kazuma becomes enraged with the organization's self-righteous attitude. He has no love for Alters that sadistically abuse their powers, but he also feels that HOLY has overstepped its authority. As he witnesses greater abuses by this special police force - not the least of which include the execution of a little girl who is discovered to have Alter abilities and the rampage of a renegade HOLY officer named George Tatsunami who has decided to take the law into his own hands - Kazuma becomes consumed with stopping HOLY. Alter-User Kazuma Torizuna may be the only one able to defy HOLY in search of the truth.

Chapter Titles

  1. Treasoner
  2. Lost Ground
  3. Attack of the Mantis Queen
  4. Ryuhou
  5. Final Shadow
  6. Excessive Justice
  7. Bullet vs. Bullet
  8. Holy

When Ryuhou confronts Kazuma, he is shocked to learn about the savage acts of George Tatsunani, but nevertheless intends to fulfill his duty as an officer of HOLY and arrest the reckless Alter User. The ensuing battle between these two Alters, separated by ideology, is interrupted by Akira and Harnish, two Alters from a rebellion group called LAWLESS, which longs to assert its own ideology on the wastelands...

More is discovered about the true nature of the LAWLESS and HOLY organizations. Conspiracies appear to abound, and to complicate matters Ryuhou is stripped of his HOLY authority, while Kazuma returns to LAWLESS headquarters with Mimori to discover it laid waste by HOLY operatives.

name: Vol. 3

description:
Ichigo knew she had cat DNA, but she never dreamed she'd transform into an actual cat! But that's just what happened one day after her heart started racing a mile a minute. Her crush, Aoyama, finds the cute kitty and takes her home! (GULP!) Ichigo is psyched to be spending time with her crush (even as a cat!), but she's worried that he'll find out her true identity. Will she ever be able to transform back to her real self and find a way to escape unnoticed?!

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 14: "Kiss and Tell"
  • Chapter 15: "Tokyo Power Tales"
  • Chapter 16: "Young Love"
  • Extra: "Tokyo Black Cat Girl"
name: Volume 4

description: The inner workings of the HOLY organization and the mysterious roots of the Alters come to light when Kazuma encounters the Alter Master Senin. Meanwhile, the SUPER HOLY officers, Mary Jane, Taiki and T.T., all under the command of Martin Zigmar, attempt to destroy Kazuma and his clan. Armed with Scryed, however, Kazuma may be a one-man army.
name: Vol. 4

description: After uncovering HOLY's plot to create an army of Alters to take over Lost Ground, battle lines are becoming clearer as once-HOLY officers begin to side with the rebellion. And in the hurly burly, Ryuhou, who joined HOLY to hunt down Alters in the first place because of his mother's murder at their hands, learns of the truth behind his mother's death. He subsequently joins Kazuma in an attack on Martin Zigmar, only to discover that yet another, more powerful Alter awaits, capable of controlling space, matter and time.
name: Vol. 5
